<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_6" id="2r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_6_r1l1"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Pfreymder </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_6_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ıeber</ex></expan> Peter als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des gelts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ Jr vns becʒaln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_6_r1l3">ſüllt / ancʒuſteen laſſen bıs von <expan>morg<ex>en</ex></expan> ſunntag <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> xıııȷ tag etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_6_r1l4"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒeıt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein ſweıgen tun in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_6_line_1588157726988_2040">der mass als Jr vns <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan> habt / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_6" id="2r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Pfreymder </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Peter, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des gelts
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir uns beczaln süllt, anczusteen
                        lassen bis von <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>morg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                sunntag</q>30.04.1419</note>
</app>
<expan>üb<ex>er</ex></expan> xiiii tag etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein
                        sweigen tun in der mass, als ir uns <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan> habt.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
